---



import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Usage Guide | Gins-Scripts"
  eyebrow="Guide"
  heading="Quick Setup"
>
  <section class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">1. URL Pattern</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/{`{Software}`}/{`{Category}`}/{`{Project}`}</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft">Example: <code>/Scripting/Widget/Countdown/index</code></p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">2. Software / Category Matrix</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>Scripting</code>: <code>Script</code>, <code>Widget</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>Scriptable</code>: <code>Widget</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>Egern</code>: <code>Script</code>, <code>Widget</code>, <code>Module</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>Stash</code>: <code>Override</code>, <code>Tile</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>Surge</code>: <code>Script</code>, <code>Module</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>Shadowrocket</code> / <code>Loon</code>: <code>Script</code>, <code>Module</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>QuantumultX</code>: <code>Rewrite</code></p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">3. Scripting Import URLs</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/Scripting/Widget/QWeather.scripting</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/Scripting/Widget/DataGovSG.scripting</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/Scripting/Widget/Countdown.scripting</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft">Source files stay under the same category path:</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>/Scripting/Widget/Countdown/index.tsx</code></p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-[20px] tracking-[-0.02em]">4. QWeather Keys</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_API_KEY</code>: your key</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_LOCATION</code>: location id or <code>lng,lat</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>QWEATHER_LANG</code>: <code>zh</code> or <code>en</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>QWEATHER_UNIT</code>: <code>m</code> or <code>i</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_API_HOST</code>: <code>https://devapi.qweather.com</code></p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-ink-soft"><code>WEATHER_NAME</code>: display city name</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
